=== Ubuntu ===

1. Install build dependecies
    For QT5:
        sudo apt-get install libqt5opengl5-dev dpkg-dev libgstreamer1.0-dev libgstreamer-plugins-base1.0-dev libqt5gstreamer1.0-dev
    For QT4:
        sudo apt-get install libqt4-opengl-dev dpkg-dev libgstreamer0.10-dev libgstreamer-plugins-base0.10-dev libqtgstreamer-dev

2. Make Makefile:
  qmake CONFIG+=dicom videomixer.pro

3. Make video mixer:
  make

4. Install
  sudo make install

=== Suse ===

1. Install build dependecies

        sudo zypper install make rpm-build qt-devel qt-gstreamer-devel libQtGlib-devel dcmtk-devel tcp_wrappers-devel openssl-devel mediainfo-devel

2. Make Makefile:
  qmake-qt4 videomixer.pro

3. Make video mixer:
  make

4. Install
  sudo make install
